Coronavirus and Trump’s Wars on Open Borders, Chinese Trade Practices, and California Homelessness 
He couldn’t have foreseen the pandemic threat, but his policies leave us better positioned to deal with it. 
Dov Fischer 
by Dov Fischer 
March 9, 2020, 5:15 AM 
